Hoya Halts Lens Plant in Thailand After Flooding

-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 
2011-10-12T08:26:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/hoya-halts-lens-plant-in-thailand-after-flooding.html
Hoya Corp. (7741)  suspended operations at a
lens plant in  Thailand  because of a possible dyke breach near
the site, according to a statement to the Tokyo Stock Exchange
today. The Japanese company said there was no damage to the
plant.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
